window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A small town age gap protector romance from a USA Today bestselling author.</p> <p>I returned to Storm Harbor for a simple job gathering intel for my best friend's security company, but my rule to keep business separate from pleasure goes up in flames when I meet my target’s niece, Petra.</p> <p>She's all innocence and sweet curves and way too good for me, which is exactly why I should resist her. In my world, distractions are deadly. And yet, when she opens that sassy mouth of hers and refuses to stay out of trouble…my resolve crumbles.</p> <p>When a hidden element takes me by surprise, turning the case, and my heart, upside down, I'm forced into a deadly game of cat-and-mouse, with Petra as the bait. The timer ticks down, closing off all my options, until I'm facing my final chance to save the woman I can't live without.</p> <p>Either I come back with her, or I don't come back at all.</p> <p>Start listening to this fast-paced romantic suspense story today!</p>"; 
